    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<br><br>醒来吧，勇敢的斗士！你不是一个人在战斗。<br>在这无尽的神秘太空站里，和伙伴同行，踏上一场无与伦比的旅程吧！<br><br>《流浪太空-online》是一款全新的合作多人在线VR游戏，延续了单人版的故事情节，为玩家带来深度的太空战斗体验。游戏目前推出PvE护航模式，未来还将推出备受期待的突击模式和生存模式。<br><br><br><br>PVE战斗由四人组成一个小队，通过不同模式下完成不同的任务，更可以收获丰富的奖励，并在正式版中通过奖励可在爬塔单机版中兑换各种酷炫的新战甲（渗透者，监察者，猎杀者），具备不同能力的特殊力场芯片（速度加成，防御加成，攻击力加成），战斗强化芯片（为多种武器属性加成等）。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/99d3cf83dd265dead238482ed06939b7.poster.avif?t=1729001700\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/99d3cf83dd265dead238482ed06939b7.webm?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/99d3cf83dd265dead238482ed06939b7.mp4?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/b0b8379ce2edf9ac7a94d948d5d5da03.poster.avif?t=1729001700\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/b0b8379ce2edf9ac7a94d948d5d5da03.webm?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/b0b8379ce2edf9ac7a94d948d5d5da03.mp4?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/663ade643d54c7fdd691afd0bcd0dd06.poster.avif?t=1729001700\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/663ade643d54c7fdd691afd0bcd0dd06.webm?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/663ade643d54c7fdd691afd0bcd0dd06.mp4?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>在护航模式中，由四人组成的小队需要协作护送神秘工程师乘上电梯逃离怪物横行的太空基地。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/957c1146ccbbdb78d7d7e3c4e934aadf.poster.avif?t=1729001700\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/957c1146ccbbdb78d7d7e3c4e934aadf.webm?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/957c1146ccbbdb78d7d7e3c4e934aadf.mp4?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/218ad2b451eda7b73b86bbbea19e18a3.poster.avif?t=1729001700\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/218ad2b451eda7b73b86bbbea19e18a3.webm?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/218ad2b451eda7b73b86bbbea19e18a3.mp4?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>护航模式玩法：<br>● 在每层楼，神秘工程师将随机在角落采集样本，玩家需一路为被保护角色提供帮助，开辟道路，以避免其受到伤害。<br>● 每层楼均有一个安全屋，玩家小队可获取治疗和补给道具。玩家需要合理利用这些资源，并在电梯启动前及时赶到电梯处。若没及时上电梯，玩家将停留在该楼层并结束当局游戏。<br>● 在最后一层楼完成采样后，电梯将因故障无法启动，玩家需要在3分钟内击毁所有无人机并保护工程师幸存。<br>● 成功通关后，玩家将获得丰厚奖励，包括各种资源并解锁新剧情。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/4b11e7a1828a2270f6a4fead0812a087.poster.avif?t=1729001700\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/4b11e7a1828a2270f6a4fead0812a087.webm?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/4b11e7a1828a2270f6a4fead0812a087.mp4?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/16441ebc2bbb424a281a0c1d2fd867ae.poster.avif?t=1729001700\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/16441ebc2bbb424a281a0c1d2fd867ae.webm?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2301800/extras/16441ebc2bbb424a281a0c1d2fd867ae.mp4?t=1729001700\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>敬请期待即将推出的其它玩法，包括突击模式、生存模式和更多基于故事的任务。<br>无论你想玩多久，请尽情享受生死轮回下的战斗快感！快去找到你的同伴，共同踏上流浪太空之旅。",
